pages.page_overview_summary: This sheet provides a detailed plan of the racking layout for the Schenker TJX project. It includes the arrangement of storage racks, sorting areas, and designated zones such as the Morgens Area. The layout is designed for the ground floor level, optimizing space for storage and operations. The drawing is part of the project documentation by Waddell Engineering Ltd., dated January 30, 2025.
